Sentencas: In order to remedy defects of thin electrolyte films, which significantly affect the power generation performance of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), the effects of pre-sintering of raw material powder (8 mol % Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2: YSZ) on the properties of the electrolyte were investigated.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: After pre-sintering YSZ powder under various temperature and time conditions, electrolytes (about 30 mu m in thickness) were deposited on the substrates of fuel electrodes by a dip-coating method and then co-sintered.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: The microstructures of the electrolytes were observed by scanning electron microscopy and laser scanning confocal microscopy.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: The power generation performance of fabricated cells was also investigated.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: As a result, the electrolyte fabricated by pre-sintering YSZ powder at 200 degrees C for 120 h was found to be dense and impermeable.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: The cell containing the electrolyte showed reasonable power generation performance.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: In the case where the pre-sintering temperature was maintained at 200 degrees C and the pre-sintering time was shortened to 20 h, the electrolyte was found to be porous, and the open circuit voltage of the cell was lower than the theoretical value.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: By increasing the pre-sintering temperature to 600 degrees C for 20 h, an ideal electrolyte could be obtained.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method

Sentencas: In contrast, the electrolyte fabricated using the YSZ powder without pre-sintering was highly porous, leading to a considerable drop in open circuit voltage.
Titulo: Effect of pre-sintering of raw material powder on properties of solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte prepared by dip-coating method
